Distance Transform for Cropping

In[59]:
zeros = np.ones_like(np.array(rgba)[...,0])
center = np.array(zeros.shape) // 2
zeros[center[0],center[1]] = 0
distance_transform = scipy.ndimage.distance_transform_edt(zeros)
